						<article class="card" id="skills">
							<h2>Technical Skills</h2>
							<p class="muted">Languages, frameworks, tools, and libraries I use daily.</p>
							<div class="pill-group">
								<span>Java</span>
								<span>Python</span>
								<span>C/C++</span>
								<span>SQL</span>
								<span>TypeScript</span>
								<span>React</span>
								<span>Spring Boot</span>
								<span>AWS</span>
								<span>PostgreSQL</span>
